 "title": "Rosé wine and strawberry jellies – pretty and fresh",
 "excerpt": "It was so hot in Hopefield this weekend that you just wanted to stay in the shade and indoors. That's when I hit on the idea of using a bottle of Rosé from the fridge to make jelly with. In the past, whenever I heard I had to work with gelatine …",
 "seo": {
  "title": "Rosé wine and strawberry jellies - pretty and fresh - Marinda Kook",
  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>It was so hot in Hopefield this weekend that you just wanted to stay in the shade and indoors.  That's when I hit on the idea of using a bottle of Rosé  from the fridge  to make jelly with.  In the past, whenever I heard I had to work with gelatine , I steered clear.  Believe me, it's as easy as stirring sugar into coffee.  The dessert looks beautiful and tastes wonderful too.  Festive for Christmas.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-045.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1014\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 045\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-045-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>YOU NEED:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 bottle sweet Rosé wine – believe me when I tell you it must be sweet<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-014.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1010\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 014\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-014-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>250 ml castor sugar ( 1 cup)<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1009\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-011-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>1   packet gelatine ( in the box are sachets, use one sachet)<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-009.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1008\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 009\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-009-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>400g strawberries or berries of your choice ( you can add more or less too)<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-004.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1007\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 004\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-004-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOW:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>pour the wine and sugar into a pot and simmer gently for 6 minutes – stir so the sugar dissolves<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-024.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1012\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-024-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>scoop  100ml of the warm wine into a cup and add the gelatine, let it stand 5  minutes and then stir through<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-027.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1013\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 027\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-027-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>pour the gelatine mixture back into the pot with the warm wine and sugar mixture, let it simmer through for about a minute</li>\n<li>wash your strawberries and trim off the stems<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-021.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1011\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 021\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-021-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>halve the strawberries</li>\n<li>arrange them in a glass or container of your choice<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-030.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1024\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 030\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-030-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>divide the wine mixture among the glasses<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-054.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1016\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 054\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-054-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>place in the fridge overnight or until set<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-057.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1017\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 057\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-057-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>It's refreshingly lovely and people think you went to a great deal of trouble.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-052.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1015\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 052\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-052-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>   Something you can prepare ahead of time for a dinner.  Truly delicious.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-137.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1019\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 137\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-137-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>You don't feel guilty polishing off this light dessert.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-155.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1021\" alt=\"aarbeijellie en lemoeneend blog 155\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/aarbeijellie-en-lemoeneend-blog-155-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>"
}
